            </div>
            <div class="pt-3 border-t border-amber-200">
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-amber-900 mb-1">🔗 URL</p>
              <div class="text-xs text-amber-700 bg-white rounded px-3 py-2 break-all max-h-20 overflow-y-auto">
